# Project Overview

This repo automates end-to-end tests for the **Invoice Canvas application** (Power Apps
Canvas app), part of the **Synergy** program.

- The Invoice app works side by side with the **Project Management** app (model-driven).
  The PM app owns **projects, partners, and contracts** and has roles like project
  manager, business development user, resource manager, and more.
- Through the Invoice app, users raise **invoices for the projects** that live in the
  Project Management app.
- **Project Managers (PMs)** are the primary users of the Invoice app; they raise
  invoices for their respective projects.

